S

Server - Class in evoter.server.http
This is a main class to start evoter server
The connection information is provided by HttpConnection bean loaded by BeanDAOFactory
Create a HttpServer and handle multi-thread HttpRequest
Server() - Constructor for class evoter.server.http.Server
 
ServerHandler - Class in evoter.server.http
This class is an extension of HttpHandler to manage HttpRequest
It receives all requests sent to Server and forward requests to correct services
After service classes finish processing request, a response is returned and it is written back client request
ServerHandler() - Constructor for class evoter.server.http.ServerHandler
 
ServerHandler.ThreadHandler - Class in evoter.server.http
This class will get parameter map from HttpExchange
and request uri and then forward this request to services
All requests has been checked UserDAO.USER_KEY to guarantee the security
except login, logout, reset password and register account requests
ServerHandler.ThreadHandler(HttpExchange) - Constructor for class evoter.server.http.ServerHandler.ThreadHandler
